{"tid":2004692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 連登愛蟈人士續個讚","createTime":"2020-05-06T15:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T15:59:40.000Z","uid":321421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08234d6114b4b974c06b61f99ceb26c8390b0ebd","tid":2004692,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"原來除咗2008嘅高登仔，我哋連登都有唔少嘅愛蟈人士㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊翻2017年睇一睇<br />\n一分鐘都冇已經有好多愛蟈巴絲留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBOEBCo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBOEBCo.png&h=093214c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一個帶大家睇下呢個咁靚仔嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5a7Lsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5a7Lsn.jpg&h=ca03afb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ByALw7o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FByALw7o.jpg&h=e89200b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8XoQJd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8XoQJd5.jpg&h=3874e103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打咁型真係我哋愛蟈人士嘅典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ELkoiNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FELkoiNr.jpg&h=f8a8ce2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n竟然係有份佔中嘅黃屍廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qH0fUkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqH0fUkN.jpg&h=d4044cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZiX7FO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZiX7FO.jpg&h=f02e1938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個唔識嘢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎重返終蟈嘅懷抱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VkoiNv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VkoiNv.jpg&h=af2fc336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSNh7FQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSNh7FQ.jpg&h=78c239cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知呢幾位巴絲係咪仲咁愛蟈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8296041935a530d16bd42d58ad78dc51070196df","tid":2004692,"uid":321421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"第二位睇下我哋I大嘅同學仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCHmQSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCHmQSM.png&h=41967ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲幫手叫多八個朋友嚟支持終蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sykC8Es.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsykC8Es.png&h=58d8f92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4A4PZL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4A4PZL8.png&h=556b4142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做咩咁話自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNU06q9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNU06q9.png&h=2484aa49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12ff7be464e46e56239ec39f3d4d4b2493d3781e","tid":2004692,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044e5cf3ee7f9285716475a7aab65e0c8540a4fa","tid":2004692,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ff7be464e46e56239ec39f3d4d4b2493d3781e","tid":2004692,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"